dnl `AC_PATH_GENERIC' (ac_path_generic.m4) by Angus Lees
dnl <gusl@cse.unsw.edu.au>. pkg-config support based on AM_PATH_GTK_2_0
dnl (gtk-2.0.m4) by Owen Taylor.
